OL,3,CWhat households need to do tonight
OL,4,Cbefore energy bill price hike
OL,6,FOfgem will increase its energy price
OL,7,Fcap on Tuesday, leaving the average
OL,8,Fhousehold paying more to stay warm,
OL,9,FITV News' Will Tullis reports
OL,11,FAlmost ten million households have
OL,12,Fbeen warned they risk overpaying for
OL,13,Ftheir energy if they do not send meter
OL,14,Freadings to their supplier before a
OL,15,F10% price rise takes effect on October
OL,16,F1.
OL,18,FThe average household energy bill will
OL,19,Fincrease by #149 a year from Tuesday
OL,20,Fas Ofgem increases its price cap, just
OL,21,Fas homes move into the winter months.
