OL,3,CWhat households need to do tonight
OL,4,Cbefore energy bill price hike
OL,6,FHouseholds with smart meters that are
OL,7,Fworking properly in smart mode do not
OL,8,Fneed to do anything as their meter
OL,9,Freadings are sent automatically to
OL,10,Fproviders.
OL,12,FHowever, households on a standard
OL,13,Fvariable tariff (SVT) and who do not
OL,14,Fhave a smart meter should submit their
OL,15,Felectricity and gas readings to their
OL,16,Fsupplier as close as possible to
OL,17,FOctober 1 to ensure any energy they
OL,18,Fuse before this date is not
OL,19,Finaccurately billed at the higher
OL,20,Fprices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
