OL,3,CWhat households need to do tonight
OL,4,Cbefore energy bill price hike
OL,6,FSuppliers who have not received meter
OL,7,Freadings base their bills on estimated
OL,8,Fusage, meaning households could be
OL,9,Foverpaying, while others may not be
OL,10,Fpaying enough.
OL,12,FComparison site Uswitch.com calculated
OL,13,Fthe average household on an SVT is
OL,14,Fexpected to spend #135 on energy in
OL,15,FOctober compared with #55 in September
OL,16,Fdue to a combination of higher rates
OL,17,Fand increased usage at the start of
OL,18,Fautumn.
