OL,3,CWhat households need to do tonight
OL,4,Cbefore energy bill price hike
OL,6,FUswitch energy spokesman Ben Gallizzi
OL,7,Fsaid: "With energy prices rising next
OL,8,Fweek, it's vital that households
OL,9,Fsubmit a meter reading, with a #19
OL,10,Fdifference between the cost of a
OL,11,Fweek's energy at September's prices
OL,12,Fcompared with October.
OL,14,F"If you delay submitting your
OL,15,Freadings, some of your September
OL,16,Fenergy usage could end up being
OL,17,Festimated and therefore charged under
OL,18,Fthe higher October rates. Try making
OL,19,Fthis task a monthly habit for billing
OL,20,Faccuracy."
