OL,4,Cbefore energy bill price hike
OL,6,F'Shop around'
OL,8,FWith the rising prices, households
OL,9,Fhave also been advised to see whether
OL,10,Fnow is the time to change their energy
OL,11,Ftariff, to beat the October price
OL,12,Fhikes.
OL,14,FOfgem chief executive Jonathan
OL,15,FBrearley urged consumers to "shop
OL,16,Faround" and consider a fixed-rate
OL,17,Ftariff that could save money, adding
OL,18,Fthat the regulator was working with
OL,19,FGovernment, suppliers, charities and
OL,20,Fconsumer groups to do "everything we
OL,21,Fcan" to support customers.
