OL,3,CWhat households need to do tonight
OL,4,Cbefore energy bill price hike
OL,6,FBen Gallizzi added: "There are a
OL,7,Fnumber of fixed tariffs worth
OL,8,Fconsidering right now. By opting for a
OL,9,Ffixed deal, you're locking in those
OL,10,Frates for the duration ` usually 12
OL,11,Fmonths ` which means households could
OL,12,Fhave price certainty and avoid the ups
OL,13,Fand downs of the price cap."
OL,15,FThe price cap sets a maximum price
OL,16,Fthat energy suppliers can charge
OL,17,Fconsumers for each kilowatt hour (kWh)
OL,18,Fof energy they use.
