OL,3,CWhat households need to do tonight
OL,4,Cbefore energy bill price hike
OL,6,FIt does not limit total bills because
OL,7,Fhouseholders still pay for the amount
OL,8,Fof energy they consume.
OL,10,FFrom October 1, households on a
OL,11,Fstandard variable tariff that pay for
OL,12,Ftheir electricity by direct debit will
OL,13,Fpay on average 24.5p per unit, with a
OL,14,Fstanding charge of 60.99p per day.
OL,16,FFor gas, the average will be 6.24p per
OL,17,Funit with a standing charge of 31.66p
OL,18,Fper day.
